quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Grief (and warning) to every Scandal-monger and backbiter
  104,2,Who piles up wealth and lays it by
  104,3,Thinking that his wealth would make him last for ever
  104,4,By no means! He will be sure to be thrown into that which breaks to pieces
  104,5,And what will explain to you that which breaks to Pieces
  104,6,(It is) the Fire of Allah lighted up (to a flame)
  104,7,The (Fire) which rises to the heart
  104,8,It shall be made to cover over them
  104,9,In pillars stretched out